WEBVTT

35:55.950 --> 35:57.950 line:80%
When you were short of meat,
you came to me for help.

35:57.950 --> 35:59.560 line:80%
Now the little brat from the Fan family is

35:59.560 --> 36:01.350 line:80%
back, and you want
to kick me out right away?

36:01.350 --> 36:03.200 line:80%
I'm telling you, no way!

36:03.200 --> 36:04.910 line:80%
You're taking this meat today,

36:04.910 --> 36:06.870 line:80%
whether you like it or not!
